Text:
Good work and thanks, 

As for the Greater Journey I know you're trying and that sooner or later it might come. 

Regardless, GREAT JOB

no greater journey still.

how about necessary secrets by Gabriel Schoenfeld? this is a pretty good book. think you could get it?

Don't know how you are managing to get these ... but many thanks for your efforts & sharing. 
If you get a chance, one of the best non-fiction books right now is Railroaded ... the kindle price is $18, which is a rip-off.

As always, thank you SO much!!!

Have you run across Miss Peregrine's Home for Peculiar Children by Ransom Riggs?  I've been looking for it all summer!
